title: The Trillionaire Mindset Trailer
description: Hosted by Ben Cahn and Emil DeRosa — a deranged Wall Street trader and his skeptical best friend — The Trillionaire Mindset highlights the funnier side of the financial world. Analyzing popular stocks and rising trends in social media, Ben and Emil dive deep into the hilarious underbelly of our economy. Check out the first episode this Monday, October 4th!
